1
00:00:14,725 --> 00:00:18,487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

2
00:00:18,562 --> 00:00:22,162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

3
00:00:22,287 --> 00:00:25,437
♪Your "same here" carries
a touch of resolve♪

4
00:00:25,862 --> 00:00:29,412
♪Pack my bags, we can set off right now♪

5
00:00:29,637 --> 00:00:33,112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

6
00:00:33,250 --> 00:00:36,712
♪The journey itself is what
truly matters before the destination♪

7
00:00:36,787 --> 00:00:40,975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

8
00:00:41,025 --> 00:00:42,612
♪Connect♪

9
00:00:42,625 --> 00:00:43,275
♪Let's go!♪

10
00:00:43,612 --> 00:00:47,137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

11
00:00:47,237 --> 00:00:50,675
♪Today, no dwelling
on negative emotions♪

12
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:53,450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

13
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:55,262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

14
00:00:55,262 --> 00:00:58,199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

15
00:00:59,075 --> 00:01:02,375
=Love In A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

16
00:01:02,675 --> 00:01:06,237
=Episode 4=

17
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:41,760
Zhu,

18
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:43,400
your brother is truly outstanding.

19
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,880
And, he's good at basketball too.

20
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:47,000
I guess.

21
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:49,720
You're truly taking this for granted.

22
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:51,120
I would be smiling in my sleep

23
00:01:51,130 --> 00:01:52,500
if I had an elder brother like him.

24
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:54,400
You can have him, then.

25
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:56,400
Take him as your elder brother.

26
00:01:57,080 --> 00:01:58,360
If you offer him to me,

27
00:01:59,380 --> 00:02:01,690
I won't be just taking him
as my elder brother, you know?

28
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,790
(He flirts with everyone in sight.)

29
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,825
(Does he think
he's a celebrity or something?)

30
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:37,240
Man, you're so good at basketball.

31
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,200
Not at all.

32
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:41,400
I was dragging the team down.

33
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,040
Not at all.

34
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:43,080
You were great.

35
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:44,320
Do you want to take a break?

36
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:49,320
I'll head to the restroom first.

37
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:53,880
Lu.

38
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:57,780
Your elder brother hasn't left yet,
you know? Where are you going?

39
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,160
That's none of your business.

40
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,080
Who made you angry?

41
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:06,000
I...

42
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,480
Who said I was angry?

43
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,600
If so, I suppose

44
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:10,800
you were bored.

45
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:14,560
Why are you so concerned about me?

46
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:17,280
Shouldn't you be concerned
with Shu Jiajia?

47
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:19,240
You two

48
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,600
were flirting with each other.

49
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:21,880
You guys were having so much fun.

50
00:03:24,440 --> 00:03:25,600
Yesterday, I briefly thought

51
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:26,800
you weren't that annoying.

52
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:28,680
But it seems like

53
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,240
I jumped to conclusions too soon.

54
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,760
So you overheard
my conversation with Mom

55
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:37,720
yesterday, you know?

56
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:42,440
You were in my house, you know?

57
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,680
I wasn't eavesdropping on you.

58
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:46,200
I...

59
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,320
Don't explain yourself to me.

60
00:03:50,425 --> 00:03:51,225
Ye Man,

61
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:53,690
what exactly are you trying to do?

62
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:54,760
That's because

63
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:56,960
you'll only hear me out when I do this.

64
00:03:57,850 --> 00:03:58,650
Fine.

65
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:00,560
Tell me, then.

66
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:02,920
What's wrong?

67
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,990
You haven't figured out
how to cover up your lie, huh?

68
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:08,160
Are you trying to tell me

69
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:10,480
that you have a hidden purpose

70
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:12,440
for every person you meet

71
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:14,960
and every action you take?

72
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,240
Or are you trying to say

73
00:04:16,690 --> 00:04:18,160
that there are many sides to you,

74
00:04:18,580 --> 00:04:20,160
and that each side of you is different?

75
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,880
Have you ever heard of
this saying before?

76
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,240
Only sincerity

77
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:30,360
can earn sincerity in return.

78
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:38,320
Do you wish to win my sincerity?

79
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:47,560
Man?

80
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:50,880
Zhu.

81
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:51,880
So you guys were here.

82
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:52,960
The second half has already started.

83
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:53,660
You should hurry.

84
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:02,080
Zhu.

85
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:05,080
Zhu,

86
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:06,480
I like your elder brother.

87
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,400
You said you liked

88
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:11,680
that kid from the Liu family last time.

89
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:14,480
That's a different story.

90
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,520
There's a unique scent on your brother.

91
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:17,760
No other people have that.

92
00:05:22,712 --> 00:05:23,832
Why didn't I detect it, then?

93
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:26,360
Only those who are in love
can detect the scent.

94
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:28,120
What scent?

95
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,640
You don't know yet.

96
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:32,160
You'll be able to detect it
once you have someone you fancy.

97
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:32,960
Let's go.

98
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:53,640
Are you full just from that?

99
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:57,080
You should be concerned
about someone else.

100
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:59,990
If you don't win Shu Jiajia's heart,
you won't be able to join Lu Group.

101
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,720
Do you have to be so mean

102
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,160
with every word you say?

103
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,040
Why are you trying to join Lu Group?

104
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,960
Will you believe me

105
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:14,480
if I say I'm joining Lu Group to learn?

106
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,520
I already investigated your background.

107
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:28,160
What have you found out?

108
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,480
I know

109
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,560
all of your secrets.

110
00:06:35,880 --> 00:06:37,080
What secret?

111
00:06:42,787 --> 00:06:44,947
Your mother tried to approach my father

112
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:47,640
when my mother was terminally ill.

113
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:51,000
Now, your father has taken his own life.

114
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,390
And, he owed people
hundreds of billions.

115
00:06:52,512 --> 00:06:54,352
Now, you're trying to approach me.

116
00:06:56,112 --> 00:06:58,512
If we link them together,

117
00:06:58,512 --> 00:07:01,087
it's easy to imagine
some sort of grand conspiracy.

118
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:08,560
Initially, I thought you were dumb.

119
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,840
But now, I didn't expect you

120
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,160
to be truly dumb.

121
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:31,600
Wait.

122
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,480
Were you calling for me?

123
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,680
Why did you tell my son all that?

124
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,800
Aren't you afraid
that my father will see you

125
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,920
in this state?

126
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:47,700
I'm going to ask you this
even if your father were around.

127
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,600
You attended my wedding

128
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:55,000
in funeral clothing.

129
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:55,880
I tolerated it.

130
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:57,480
You looked down on me
and disrespected me.

131
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,560
I tolerated that as well.

132
00:07:58,560 --> 00:08:00,400
But what gives you
the right to tell my son

133
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:01,760
that I seduced your father?

134
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:02,480
What gives?

135
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:04,440
Isn't that the truth?

136
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:05,840
Let me ask you this, then.

137
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:07,640
Who was the one
who crawled into my father's bed

138
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:08,960
when my mother was pregnant?

139
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,440
And who was it
who took a desperate gamble

140
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:12,760
when my mother was gravely ill,

141
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:13,920
causing her to give me away...

142
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,640
I mean, causing her illness to worsen,

143
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:17,800
passing away soon after that.

144
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,480
My mother was kind to you.

145
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,200
What did she get in the end?

146
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:24,120
In the end,

147
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:26,320
her husband became your husband.

148
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:29,360
What was supposed to be her life
end up becoming yours.

149
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:30,640
And now,

150
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:31,800
you want your son

151
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,280
to steal my position as well!

152
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,760
Aren't you afraid of karma at all?

153
00:08:36,920 --> 00:08:38,600
Listen up.

154
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:41,160
My mother is the only person
my father will ever love.

155
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,600
And you?

156
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:45,200
You're just a shameless usurper.

157
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,920
You're just her replacement
when he gets lonely!

158
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:47,800
Nonsense!

159
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:51,440
Lu!

160
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:54,920
Mom, what are you doing?

161
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,640
Zhu is hurt.

162
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:04,890
I'll take her to bandage her wound.

163
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,440
Why are you so kind to me?

164
00:09:45,660 --> 00:09:47,250
It's because you're my younger sister.

165
00:09:48,500 --> 00:09:50,080
I don't want to be your younger sister.

166
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:54,240
What do you want to be, then?

167
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,440
Your mother hit me.

168
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,760
Now, you're dressing my wound.

169
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:02,520
Are you playing the savior here?

170
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:05,520
What? Am I playing the savior

171
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:07,280
by dressing your wound?

172
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:14,680
I don't want your mother to see this.

173
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,850
Avoid contact with water
for the next few days.

174
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:33,480
That hurts.

175
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:35,240
I'll be gentle, then.

176
00:10:45,787 --> 00:10:50,287
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

177
00:10:50,512 --> 00:10:54,300
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

178
00:10:54,475 --> 00:10:58,550
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

179
00:10:58,550 --> 00:11:02,687
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

180
00:11:02,812 --> 00:11:06,587
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

181
00:11:06,587 --> 00:11:10,362
♪I'll learn to stop
longing for what's gone♪

182
00:11:10,362 --> 00:11:12,637
♪The you in my memories♪

183
00:11:12,637 --> 00:11:14,650
♪Will fade from clarity♪

184
00:11:14,650 --> 00:11:20,087
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

185
00:11:21,650 --> 00:11:27,087
♪Forget you completely♪
